articles.title: European probe clicks stunning pictures to mark 25,000 orbits around Mars - India Today
articles.description: Since its arrival in late 2003 Mars Express has changed our understanding of Mars offering unprecedented insights into its atmosphere surface and moons
articles.content:
The European Space Agency's (ESA) Mars Express orbiter has completed its 25,000th orbit around Mars, capturing a breathtaking high-altitude view of the planet to commemorate the achievement.
